{"tid":1463093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［有鬼］示威現場有鬼 連登一樣可以","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:39:05.000Z","uid":23378,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab8392b5b453c0634b257cdda3c586f0b802d706","tid":1463093,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"呢兩日見到連登咁多自己人屌自己人 <br />\n<br />\n真係心諗做乜撚 但係大家諗深一層<br />\n<br />\n分化緊我地除左三毛 仲有可能係警犬都開始混入我地當中<br />\n<br />\n比起實際係現場比你捉耳機 匿係螢幕後面挑撥離間更安全<br />\n<br />\n大家記住 我地敵人一致對外<br />\n<br />\n係呢個仆街政權<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆</span><br />\n<br />\n齊心就事成<br />\n<br />\n唔好係呢個時候散啊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"153e8519b405ca38d13634d692dc07a2bdf53ad1","tid":1463093,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:09:46.000Z","msg":"不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725a1058ca302dd325f148317852df45db90f88b","tid":1463093,"uid":116105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"共產黨以分化、抹黑起家<br />\n各位唔好輕易中計<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 對準政權 </span>"},{"pid":"bd533d468e5f31b63e8090690f0660e784aa18f5","tid":1463093,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"醒啲啊香港人"},{"pid":"d3fee75c4221d3db693733f2ac3c127a20303a4b","tid":1463093,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:16:20.000Z","msg":"你唔同意佢個做法無問題<br />\n但唔好屌人係鬼<br />\n<br />\n唔岩傾到岩"},{"pid":"5858d09c1532b3512cbc4bda8ed5cf2194739b7a","tid":1463093,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3fee75c4221d3db693733f2ac3c127a20303a4b","tid":1463093,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score